Description
Animal
Class, which represents an animal with a name, commands it knows, and its date of birth.
AnimalController
Class is responsible for controlling the actions related to animals, such as creating, updating, deleting, and training animals.
AnimalCreator
This class is responsible for creating new animal objects based on the provided animal type, name, and date of birth.

Class which is representing a repository for managing animals.

Class - enum represents the different types of animals that can be created.
